{"tid":44710,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"好孤獨","createTime":"2016-12-18T13:08:35.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-18T16:34:10.000Z","uid":28484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e5203b85564bf504b115af1aebdb24dee49443fb","tid":44710,"uid":28484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T13:08:35.000Z","msg":"以前覺得同成幫朋友一齊會好開心只係一時開心<br />\n但開始冇乜心機搵，因為冇人明白我<br />\n呢排先覺得原來我係咁獨<br />\n可能小學六年既經歷，可以望著雙腳過六年<br />\n試過會自己一個人獨到喊<br />\n而家習慣自己一個睇戲行街打波<br />\n但心底裡想搵一個明白我既人陪伴我，唔知成世人會唔會遇到<br />\n<br />\n我發現好識保護自己，對住咩人都會笑出嚟，但唔係真正開心笑"},{"pid":"5946bdfbfc0965c25230fe7931f5e60b50f8e640","tid":44710,"uid":59501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T13:10:10.000Z","msg":"I know that feel bro"},{"pid":"5377966344dd6a2ff77375eb4d77e0f93196ad51","tid":44710,"uid":18320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T13:10:25.000Z","msg":"屌你老母留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nMe too"},{"pid":"06b63bfd7bdc3728eb34561c3bf108aa77eb7b15","tid":44710,"uid":28484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T13:12:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>I know that feel bro</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n謝，你又如何過日子"},{"pid":"d92157b145756baea9a4b8c697c09ceecf0b54f7","tid":44710,"uid":52816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T14:17:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"74b7ee51de35c623a173aadb8ccb57ce608459d7","tid":44710,"uid":2154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T15:03:03.000Z","msg":"好撚明白你 可telegram 我"},{"pid":"7dcd56bdcfe19cbdd57dac0f9ac36d0df02962c9","tid":44710,"uid":2154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T15:05:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://telegram.me/iamnotaman\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftelegram.me%2Fiamnotaman&d=HeJvc9wm17QykqK%2Be%2FRS0ksIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=578325f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://telegram.m